extends layout

block content
  section.info-card
    h1 Frequently Asked Questions

    h2 Is the payment system real?
    p No. Checkout is mocked for the project. The website saves the order, but it does not charge a real card.

    h2 How long does shipping take?
    p Since this is a class project, shipping is fake. In our fake company story, orders ship in 3 to 5 business days.

    h2 Can I return a mystery box?
    p Our fake refund policy allows returns within 14 days if the box is unopened.

    h2 Are the products real?
    p The products are sample mystery boxes stored in our SQLite database.

    h2 Why do I need an account?
    p Accounts let the website save your mock orders and show your purchase history on the profile page.
